{{!--
    Text template for invite email
    ==============================

    Available params:

      {{{recepient.name}}}: The full name of the receiving user.

      {{{recepient.firstName}}}: The first name of the receiving user.

      {{{recepient.lastName}}}: The last name of the receiving user.

      {{{invitor.name}}}: The full name of the inviting user.

      {{{invitor.firstName}}}: The first name of the inviting user.

      {{{invitor.lastName}}}: The last name of the inviting user.

      {{{realm.represents}}}: The entity type that the realm represents (e.g. "Todo list" or "Chat group").

      {{{realm.name}}}: The name of the realm.

      {{{realm.<arbritrary realm property>}}}: Any property from the realm being invited to.

      {{{realm.realmId}}}: The realmId being invited to.

      {{{acceptUrl}}}: The URL to navigate to in order to accept the invite.

      {{{rejectUrl}}}: The URL to navigate to in order to reject the invite.

      {{{app.name}}}: The name of the app.

      {{{app.url}}}: The URL of the app.

      {{{app.isWebPage}}}: True if the app is a web page, false if it's an app.

--}}
Hi {{{recepient.firstName}}},

{{{invitor.firstName}}} invited you to {{{realm.represents}}} called {{{realm.name}}}.

You can accept the invite next time you {{#if app.isWebPage}}visit {{{app.url}}}{{else}}open the {{{app.name}}}{{/if}}

You can also navigate to {{{acceptUrl}}} to accept the invite.
